          </a></li>
        <li><a href="#projects">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M216 40h-80V24a8 8 0 0 0-16 0v16H40a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v120a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h39.36l-21.61 27a8 8 0 0 0 12.5 10l29.59-37h56.32l29.59 37a8 8 0 1 0 12.5-10l-21.61-27H216a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V56a16 16 0 0 0-16-16M104 144a8 8 0 0 1-16 0v-24a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Zm32 0a8 8 0 0 1-16 0v-40a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Zm32 0a8 8 0 0 1-16 0V88a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/></svg>
          </a></li>
        <li><a href="#cv">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.414A2 2 0 0 0 15.414 6L12 2.586A2 2 0 0 0 10.586 2zm5 6a1 1 0 1 0-2 0v3.586l-1.293-1.293a1 1 0 1 0-1.414 1.414l3 3a1 1 0 0 0 1.414 0l3-3a1 1 0 0 0-1.414-1.414L11 11.586z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
